name: CliKintoneTest-17 Should return the error message when the user information is incorrect
fullName: features/common.feature#CliKintoneTest-17 Should return the error message when the user information is incorrect

steps.name: When I run the command with args "record export --base-url $$TEST_KINTONE_BASE_URL --app 1 --username abc --password abc"
Then I should get the exit code is non-zero
And The output error message should match with the pattern: "\[401\] \[CB_WA01\] Password authentication failed."

labels.name: suite
labels.value: CliKintoneTest-17 Should return the error message when the user information is incorrect
